summary: what the characters from moomin would do if they played minecraft: moomintroll: he loves going on adventures with his friends,...
body:
what the characters from moomin would do if they played minecraft:

moomintroll: he loves going on adventures with his friends, although he gets sidetracked at the opportunity to befriend an animal. he takes a lot of screenshots and is eager to complete the main storyline

moominpappa: goes on grand expeditions and always keeps a journal on him, making sure to record everything that happens (although he exaggerates sometimes)

moominmamma: makes giant farms and has a near endless supply of food. she loves creating flowerbeds and baking cakes

snufkin: he spends most of his time traveling. if he finds a place of interest or needs to heal, he makes a dirt house and goes fishing

little my: she makes sure that no one keeps any secrets (at least, not from her, anyways). often goes on expeditions with sniff and loves aggravating mobs (ESPECIALLY endermen and zombie pigmen)

sniff: searches for diamonds and structures (things like mansions, sunken ships, etc). however he refuses to go on expeditions alone, so he often searches for villages to trade. prefers playing on peaceful mode

snork: loves to make marvelous buildings and refuses to play on creative. his game has a lot of mods installed so he can push his creativity to the limit

snorkmaiden: she would spend her days flower picking and collecting wool and her nights decorating her house. always has the most beautiful home

hemulen: primarily goes out collecting, although a fair amount of his time goes to trying to find every single recipe in the game. his house is full of armor stands and item frames

stinky: steals items and uses any diamonds he can obtain to make a hoe
